General.Name: Union Pioneer Public Company Limited
General.Description: Union Pioneer Public Company Limited manufactures and distributes finished elastic products in Thailand, the United States, and internationally. The company offers rubber threads for use in the rims of baby and adult diaper's legs and waist; rubber tapes; elastic braids; elastic webbing and crochet; covering yarn products; and elastics for cloth and disposable facemasks. It also provides elastic for car seat components, such as braided cords and woven straps are used to fasten parts and vehicle interiors in the automotive industry. In addition, the company offers elastic for medical devices, including Esmarch and elastic bandages; non-sterile conforming bandage; tourniquet; and anti-slip, as well as elastic bands for exercise and physical therapy. It offers its products under the VENUS brand. The company was founded in 1973 and is headquartered in Bangkok, Thailand. Union Pioneer Public Company Limited is a subsidiary of Saha-Union Public Company Limited.
